ContextEventType ccaffeine.ce.ComponentInstanceDeleteRequestEvent.getContextEventType (   ) 
 

Returns the integer standard type for the event.

If the event is not one of the standard types, then this returns ContextEventType.NONE. For ComponentInstanceDeleteRequestEvent, the type is ComponentDeletePending.
